organization.description:
Kingswood Community Transport provides accessible vehicles for people who cannot easily use public transport or who are transport-disadvantaged.

KCT's Dial-&-Ride service will allow you to:

Visit Family and Friends;

Keep doctor and dental appointments;

Play an active part in the community.

The service covers return trips to all hospitals, there is an additional charge for this service. Please speak to the office for further information. The Doctors Shuttle provides trips, both ways, to doctor's surgeries, dentists, opticians and other services residents need.
